5.1. You may browse our Site without providing your personal information.
5.1.1. Data you provide us with. Through our Site, you may provide us with your Personal Data to send your project request or to send your career request. Data which you may provide to us include:
5.1.2. Full name;
5.1.3. Phone number;
5.1.4. Email address;
5.1.5. City;
5.1.6. CV;
5.1.7. Portfolio;
5.2.1. Data collected automatically. We use this data to constantly improve our site. Therefore, when you access our Site, certain data may be collected automatically. Such data include:
5.2.2. Cookies.
5.2.3. Device data (device model, OS type etc.);
5.2.4. IP address;
5.2.5. Connection type (WiFi, LTE, 3G);
5.2.6. Language and region;
5.2.7. Your interactions with Site.
5.3. If you sign up to a newsletter list, you will be sent what you asked for. We operate “double opt-in” lists and you will need to reconfirm your subscription before anything is sent. You can unsubscribe at any time by clicking the unsubscribe button on any email.
5.4. You are not automatically subscribed to any other lists, but may be invited to join an appropriate one.
5.5. If you make an enquiry via our site, we will keep details of that enquiry and response for our data retention period.
5.6. We do not routinely keep special category data.  To the extent we hold this, it was supplied or made publicly available by you.
5.7. Automatically collected data is aggregated and anonymized.
